snippet.title: Mindful Music
snippet.description:
Just fresh music.

===========================

• Music submissions: Please use the e-mail below for track, album or mix submissions. Please allow 1-2 business days for a response.

• Contact via e-mail or Facebook is preferred for all other business inquiries over the YouTube messaging system as I seldom check it. 

• As always, please stay Mindful, discover, share, and inspire! Peace.

===========================

Disclaimer: All music posted is for promotional use only most of which is acquired via submissions and permission from artist/producer. If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to send an e-mail. Thank you!
